data.description: Cute 3 bedroom, 2 bath single level home located at the end of a cul-de-sac and on a huge 5,240 square foot lot.  Very well maintained and freshly painted. Featuring 18X'18" ceramic tile flooring throughout the home,  Split system air conditioner in the primary bedroom and a window a/c in the living room and bedroom. Parking up to 6 cars- 2 in carport and 4 in driveway. Leased PV keeps electricity bill low. Make this your home today!
